@DATABASE MUIVideo
@NODE Main "Overview"
@$VER: MUIVideo_eng.guide 2.33 (11.09.98)

MUIVideo - A Video Database
==============================

MUIVideo is a film database, its user interface was
designed using @{"MUI" LINK MUI}.

Contents:

 @{"Disclaimer            " LINK Disclaimer}  Status etc.
 @{"Systemrequirements    " LINK requirements}  Hard & soft requirements
 @{"Installation          " LINK Installation}  Installation on harddisk
 @{"Start                 " LINK Start}  Getting startet, parameters
 @{"How to use            " LINK Howtouse}  Working with MUIVideo
 @{"What to do            " LINK Ablauf}  Introduction
 @{"Keyboard              " LINK Keyboard}  How to use the keyboard
 @{"ARexx                 " LINK ARexx}  The ARexx-port

 @{"History               " LINK History}  History
 @{"Known bugs            " LINK Bugs}  Known bugs
 @{"ToDo-List             " LINK ToDo}  What I want to add
 @{"Thanks                " LINK Danke}  Thanks
 @{"Author                " LINK author}  Information about the author (ADDRESS CHANGED!)


@ENDNODE
