see also: @{"STARTMUINAMES" LINK A_Startmuinames}
@ENDNODE
@NODE A_Startmuinames "STARTMUINAMES"

STARTMUINAMES

Starts the plug-in "MUINames".

see also: @{"STARTMUITAPES" LINK A_Startmuitapes}
@ENDNODE
@NODE A_Sleep "SLEEP"

SLEEP

Cancels input of the user, the sleep-pointer (normally the watch)
is shown.

see also: @{"WAKE" LINK A_Wake}
@ENDNODE
@NODE A_Wake "WAKE"

WAKE

Allows input by the user again, the normal mouse-pointer
is shown again.

see also @{"SLEEP" LINK A_Sleep}
@ENDNODE

